## Modules

### 1. Reinforcement Learning (`rl`)
- **Environments**: GridWorld, FrozenLake, Taxi
- **Algorithms**: Monte Carlo, TD(0), Policy Iteration, Value Iteration
- **Visualization**: Convergence plots, policy visualization

